title: Scp 8642 16
content:
Congrats, you found the secret page! How did you get here? There aren’t any links to this page on any of the other pages. Really this page only exists because I miscounted the number of pages I’d need and I didn’t feel like re-numbering them. The only way you could’ve found this page would be to have input the url for the 16th offset page manually into your browser, which means you either:

A. Found every offset page and noticed number 16 was missing, or
B. Went through all the offset pages in order to find all 7 endings like a dirty cheater.

Well, either way, you showed some smarts, so I guess I’ll reward you. Here, have a flow chart of all the possible paths:
